{"tid":232632,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣樂評：周杰倫的音樂才華其實是高於Eminem","createTime":"2017-05-07T01:36:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-12T02:03:13.000Z","uid":100680,"like":3,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4606c005bf640168214f59197a60a966ecb95e73","tid":232632,"uid":100680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T01:36:50.000Z","msg":"埃米納姆（Eminem），原名Marshall Bruce Mathers III。1972年10月17日出生在密蘇里州的堪薩斯城，美國說唱歌手。人們喜歡他為痞子阿姆。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/large/486000210497e03cab5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2Flarge%2F486000210497e03cab5&h=b475e380&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n阿姆從1997年出道至今，獲獎無數，更是格萊美的常客，他為好萊塢電影創作的歌曲經常在奧斯卡上被提名。他打破了只有黑人才能玩好說唱的定律，獨特的鼻音辨認度極高。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/large/48300021eb7264ad287\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2Flarge%2F48300021eb7264ad287&h=8285c255&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n周杰倫在出道時拽拽的性格和阿姆很像，音樂上也是獨樹一幟，在風格上杰倫的饒舌也是自成一派，在音樂才華上杰倫其實是高於阿姆的，杰倫精通多種樂器，尤其鋼琴是彈的出神入化；創作上，阿姆其實是比不上周杰倫的，杰倫在亞洲地區所獲的獎項不勝枚舉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/large/48500025c5163f9f036\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2Flarge%2F48500025c5163f9f036&h=5ccc8a07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n音樂王子周杰倫唯獨沒有獲得過格萊美，周杰倫也曾在訪談中談到，最想得到的獎項是格萊美年度最佳專輯獎，他希望格萊美上有中國人獲獎。把音樂帶到世界各個角落是他的畢生追求。也祝杰倫早日把中國風的音樂帶到世界的舞台上。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/large/48400025f4e10b4ff18\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2Flarge%2F48400025f4e10b4ff18&h=1bce423e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/entertainment/eoog.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fentertainment%2Feoog.html&d=ZAqn3h4t0e4XfOyVRCtvGDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=4e48c920\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/entertainment/eoog.html</a>"},{"pid":"41f577bfb4627be015787c23610dd2fb46b8d6d8","tid":232632,"uid":44289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T01:41:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />rap得好過em"},{"pid":"424f83464b5a5519fe5db6ed6ab8a1b2940d6ee5","tid":232632,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T01:49:15.000Z","msg":"哎？很屌喔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"562b119796f095b022d1ecd9ee2d7c0a692853e5","tid":232632,"uid":56401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T01:52:29.000Z","msg":"唔撚同風格都可以比"},{"pid":"af4a2cebd6aa00b6731e2c91fac553a62a4075d7","tid":232632,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T01:53:54.000Z","msg":"chka chka Slim Shady"},{"pid":"535a4381a40a5bfff5050a5c6f47a14621656d88","tid":232632,"uid":95516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T02:15:26.000Z","msg":"世界十大笑話"},{"pid":"d9537c4f752940f1331b50d169fc8e8b71c3f182","tid":232632,"uid":20170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T02:18:21.000Z","msg":"台灣世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eee542c2d69c0b8dc7ab8f26421f0ffc9205c0ec","tid":232632,"uid":26942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T02:19:04.000Z","msg":"他希望格萊美上有中國人獲獎。 <br />\n台灣 邊到來？"},{"pid":"ca27d3cc272fc211ded15aa0bb7ed1fe19d9121f","tid":232632,"uid":3748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T02:49:03.000Z","msg":"又亞洲舞王<br />\n又音樂鬼才<br />\n台灣特別多飛機師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a825382aff817b7bcca4eec6db1d7df66b4b040c","tid":232632,"uid":23021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T02:49:36.000Z","msg":"你